PPL_MOE_SETTINGS_SHOW_PRONOUNS_DESCRIPTI: Show ppl.moe pronouns at the top of the user's message
PPL_MOE_SETTINGS_HIDE_PRONOUNDB_DESCRIPT: Hide PronounDB's pronouns if there are ppl.moe ones present
Install PronounDB for this setting to be relevant
PPL_MOE_SETTINGS_SHOW_PROFILE_BADGE_DESC: Show a ppl.moe badge next to a user's name if they have a ppl.moe profile. This will display independently of pronouns.
PPL_MOE_SETTINGS_USER_MODAL_ICON_DESCRIP: Display an icon instead of text for the User Modal tab.
PPL_MOE_CONNECTION_DISCONNECT_CONTENT: You cannot disconnect your ppl.moe profile from your Discord account.
PPL_MOE_CONNECTION_VISIBILITY_CONTENT: Profile visibility cannot be changed in Discord.
